     H            Y.
     F** AB#R432B *******************************************
     F* SERVICE PARTS - LAUNCH IAF VS SCS ORDER COMPARE     *
     F*    LEC.  2022.08.17                                 *
     F*******************************************************
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W#PGM
     I                                      244 253 W#WSID
     I                                      254 263 W#USER
     I                                      264 269 W#JBNO
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WTIME
     I                                        7  140SDATE
     I                                        7  100SDYY
     I                                       11  120SDMM
     I                                       13  140SDDD
     I                                        1   60STIME
     I                                        1   20STHH
     I                                        3   40STMM
      *
     I I            'AB#R432FX'               1  10 FIXPGM
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * MAIN                                               *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C                     TIME           WTIME
      *
     C                     MOVELSDATE     CURDAT
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   SHPDAT
      *
     C                     CALL 'UTLR10'
     C                     PARM           CURDAT  8
     C                     PARM '+'       SIGN    1
     C                     PARM '0002'    DAYS    4
     C                     PARM 'Y'       IAFNO   1
     C                     PARM           SHPDAT  8
     C                     PARM           RTN     1
      *
     C                     CALL 'AB#C432'
     C                     PARM           SHPDAT
      *
      ***                  CALL FIXPGM
      ***                  PARM           SHPDAT
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *----------------------------------------------------*
